processStates.name: LaharService
processStates.description: The lahar service returns the area inundated by lahars of the Cotopaxi volcano, and relies on pre-calculated simulation results for flow height, flow velocity, flow pressure, erosion, and deposition. The simulation software used for lahar modelling is the physically based numerical model RAMMS::DEBRIS FLOW.
